Package: Rcsvg
Type: Package
Title: An Easy Way to Glue Multiple CSV Files with Common Headers into a Single Data Frame   
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("John", "Piper", email =  "john.piper.using.r@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A convenient way to join, like a union all, multiple CSV files from a folder path 
	into a single data frame to modify and export.  You can also glue multiple common 
	data frames from list into single data frame.
